<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PeruTM3.2">
<l>nūli ṉēriṭai yārtiṟat tēniṟkum</l>
<l>ñālan taṉṉoṭuṅ kūṭuva tillaiyāṉ</l>
<l>āliyāvaḻaiyā varaṅkā veṉṟu</l>
<l>māle ḻuntoḻin tēṉeṉtaṉ mālukkē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>There will be no associating, for me, with the world</l>
<l>that remains by the side of women with waists finer than thread.</l>
<l>Dancing, calling out loud ‘O Raṅga!’</l>
<l>I have ended up with desire rising for my own Māl.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
